	<description><![CDATA[
	<p>This is a responsive, 'mobile first' HTML5 template from <a href="http://kisswebdesign.co.uk">KISS Web Design</a>.</p><p>It incorporates the hard work of many talented people. It was forked from <a href="https://github.com/nternetinspired/OneWeb">OneWeb Project on GitHub</a>.</p><p>I have taken that a great baseline for building this template, adding my own bits along the way.</p><p>Thanks goes to those who went before me:<br />Notably, this template takes the HTML5 goodness and awesome polyfills from the <a href="http://html5boilerplate.com/">HTML5 Boilerplate</a> of Paul Irish.<br />The mobile first logic and sexy typographic basics from <a href="http://www.stuffandnonsense.co.uk/projects/320andup/">320 and up</a> by Andy Clarke.<br />Some really neat Joomla! tricks and Google Font awesomeness from Matt Thomas' <a href="http://construct-framework.com/">Construct Framework</a>.<br /> The fluid <a href="http://cssgrid.net/">1140px Grid</a> grid from Andy Taylor.<br />And especially the work of Seth Warburton @nternetinspired <a href="http://internet-inspired.com">Internet Inspired!</a> for pulling it all together, adding his own flair and creating the original OneWeb template.</p>
	]]></description>
		
